summary: A comprehensive test suite that verifies Django's delete behavior across a wide range of scenarios, including cascade deletions for foreign keys, many-to-many through tables, generic relations, transaction handling, concurrent access locking, large batch deletions, ordered deletions, and proxy model on_delete semantics, as well as specific regression cases.
business_intent: To prevent regressions and ensure reliable, correct handling of delete operations in the Django ORM under diverse relationship configurations and edge cases.
